
SHOWBIZ and football stars descended on Hamilton yesterday as actor Gianni Capaldi married former cheerleader Amanda Fitz.
Actor Martin Compston and former Chelsea defender Mario Melchiot were best men at the ceremony.
Later, the wedding party posed for pictures at Chatelherault Country Park.
 

Gianni, 39, who grew up in Hamilton, played youth football for Motherwell before becoming an actor.
His footballing guests included Murdo MacLeod, John Hartson and Kris Commons, whose daughter April was a flower girl at the ceremony.
 

